values  (1, 'Monster Energy Ultra Vice Guava, Sugar Free Energy Drink, 16 Ounce (Pack of 15)', 'Monster Energy Store', 'Miami has it all, mind-blowing Latin energy, premier racing from NASCAR to F1, and world class beaches with the hottest clubs right on the sand. Whether youre an over-the-top partier or an undercover crime fighter in a pastel suit, T-shirt, and loafers - you gotta stay energized! From South Beach to Calle Ocho, looking good and feeling good is what its all about. With zero sugar to weigh you down, the fresh taste of perfectly ripened guava, and our world-famous Monster Energy blend, Ultra Vice Guava has you covered.', 29.87, 29.87, 'In Stock', 'Grocery & Gourmet Food › Beverages › Bottled Beverages, Water & Drink Mixes › Energy Drinks', '2.6 x 2.6 x 6.2 inches; 16.6 Pounds', '2000-01-01', 'Monster Energy', 'USA', 4.60, 191, 80, 11, 2, 2, 5),
