        (165, 'Rejuvenate Muscle Building Drink Sticks – Patented EAAs, 1 Stick = 40g Whey Protein Isolate, 11x Better Than Whey Protein, GLP-1 + Bariatric Approved*, Raspberry, 14 Count', 'Rejuvenate Muscle Health Store', 'Product Description Introducing Rejuvenate Muscle Activator, the ultimate patented plant-based drink for any lifestyle! Our formula contains only essential muscle-building components, providing the optimal fuel for your workouts and daily routine. Say goodbye to additives and enjoy the refreshing, delicious taste of Rejuvenate today! HOW DOES IT WORK?                                        Unlike traditional whey protein powders, Rejuvenate Muscle Activator does not require your body to break down protein. Instead, it provides pure EAAs in a precise patented ratio - the building blocks of protein—ready for immediate absorption. This means more effective muscle support! CLINICALLY PROVEN BENEFITS: 11x More Effective Than Whey Protein Isolate (gram per gram comparison): Rejuvenate is clinically shown to increase muscle protein synthesis by 57% (even at rest!). It’s the ultimate choice for muscle maintenance, especially for GLP-1 + Bariatric users. Low-Calorie, High-Impact: At just 5 calories per serving, Rejuvenate provides all the muscle-building benefits without the excess calories found in traditional whey protein shakes. Easy on the Stomach: Many GLP-1 + bariatric users struggle with digestion post-surgery. Rejuvenate’s plant-based formula is designed to be gentle on your digestive system, with zero sugars, fillers, or carbs. Powered by Promino: This patented formula leverages 20 years of research and provides a scientifically optimized ratio of essential amino acids to maximize muscle growth and recovery. A single 3.6g serving of Rejuvenate Muscle Activator has the same muscle-building power as 40g of whey protein isolate!       SO WHERE’S THE PROTEIN?       When you eat protein, your body must first break it down to extract the amino acids used to grow and repair muscle fibers. Rejuvenate Muscle Activator provides your body with these protein building blocks directly, without the excess calories, filler, carbohydrates and uptake delay of whey and other protein sources. DIAAS (Digestible Indispensable Amino Acid Score) is a scoring system recently adopted by the World Health Organization. It’s the gold standard for measuring protein quality.       DIAAS looks at the essential amino acid (EAA) content/composition in a protein source (per gram) and compares them to the body’s minimum requirements of each while also taking into consideration absorption rates (as not everything you eat is absorbed the same way). Yep, protein quality is all about the EAAs.       A DIAAS (score) of 100% would provide the EAAs in a ratio that would satisfy your body’s average requirement of these amino acids (should you consume 0.66 g/kg/day of this protein).       We’ve provided the DIAAS for many protein sources above and as you can see, Rejuvenate Muscle Activator rises above with a 321% DIAAS!       How? Well, Rejuvenates optimized ratio and amounts of EAAs along with its lightning-fast absorption rates allows our post-workout formula to score a higher DIAAS.       Reference:       Wolfe RR, et al. Protein quality as determined by the Digestible Indispensable Amino Acid Score: evaluation of factors underlying the calculation. Nutr Rev. 2016 Sep;74(9):584-99. CLINICALLY PROVEN: The Rejuvenate Muscle Activator formula has been shown to be 60 percent more effective than whey and leading proteins for building and retaining lean muscle. Our essential amino acid supplements are shown to support muscle health for recovery and strength.       REJUVENATE YOUR LIFE: Has zero sugar, zero fat, only 5 calories, and is a plant based formula that will not cause stomach upset like typical whey. Rejuvenate is also keto friendly and gluten free.       SCIENTIFICALLY BACKED: Rejuvenate has a global patent that is backed by 20+ years of clinical research. Rejuvenate is shown to increase muscle protein synthesis even at rest, being the key factor in muscle maintenance and growth.       OPTIMIZED PROTEIN COMPONENTS: Rejuvenate is a new and innovative blend of essential amino acids that mixes easily with water and comes in convenient single serve sticks. It can be added to your smoothie or enjoyed as a refreshing fruit drink after your daily activity or between meals.       RAPID MUSCLE GROWTH: Rejuvenate provides a pure 100 percent optimized protein component formula that is designed for maximum muscle growth potential and has faster absorption rates than other muscle health supplements for men and women.', 24.99, 0.00, 'In Stock', 'Grocery & Gourmet Food › Beverages › Bottled Beverages, Water & Drink Mixes › Meal Replacement & Protein Drinks › Protein Drinks', '2.56 x 3.07 x 5.28 inches; 3.84 ounces', '2000-01-01', 'Element Nutrition Inc.', null, 4.20, 392, 61, 18, 7, 6, 8),
