        (252, 'Sincerely Nuts - Dried Turkish Apricots | One Lb. Bag | Healthy Pitted Apricot Fruit | Raw Vegan Snack | Dehydrated | Sweet Gourmet Snacking Food | Kosher and Gluten Free', 'Sincerely Nuts Store', 'From the brand Previous page Welcome to Sincerely Nuts, where we care about adding the freshest snacks to your pantry since 2002. Our nutritious nuts, dried fruits, snack trays and more are the result of our dedication to you.          Our products are packed with essential nutrients designed to boost your overall health and well-being. Thank you for choosing Sincerely Nuts! Our Commitment                                        Our unwavering commitment is to consistently offer the finest industry-leading service, convenience, and reliability, ensuring every individual who savore Sincerely Nuts experiences nothing short of excellence. Our Location                                        Operating from our cutting-edge establishment in New Jersey, we are dedicated to providing exceptional snack products that are unparalleled in quality, freshness, and taste, delivered directly to your doorstep. Next page Product Description Our Philosophy       We love nuts!       Sincerely Nuts isn’t just our namesake, it’s the entire foundation of our organization’s identity. We make sure that every single delicious and savory product we offer passes the family and friends test. That means if we aren’t comfortable sharing a product with our family, friends and loved ones then we aren’t comfortable trying to sell it to our amazing customers.       Customers, just like you, are the reason we exist and the reason we love coming into work each and every day. From our Sincerely Nuts home base in New York City, we truly strive to deliver only the finest, freshest and, most delectable nut and snack products right to your door. We also strive to always deliver convenience and reliability for every single person who enjoys Sincerely Nuts.       Our Promise to You       We are here for you. We are only here because of you. We will do what it takes to keep you Sincerely Nuts! Sincerely Nuts - Dried Turkish Apricots                                         Healthy Pitted Apricot Fruit | Raw Vegan Snack | Dehydrated | Sweet Gourmet Snacking Food | Kosher and GluteGluten-Freen Free History of Apricots                                           Apricots have been found and enjoyed wild and grown since as far back as prehistoric times. The scientific name ‘Prunus armeniaca’ is derived from Armenia, where most scientists believe apricots originated. However, they were also present in ancient Greece and Rome, and many other experts claim that original large scale cultivation could have happened in India over 3,000 years ago. Enjoy the same sweet & satisfying dried fruit snack that’s been winning people over for centuries! Nutrient Profile                                           Sincerely Nuts dried apricots are full of healthy dietary fiber for digestive regularity, as well as free-radical fighting antioxidants. Benefit from a dose of vitamins and minerals including:       · Potassium       · Calcium       · Magnesium       · Iron       · Copper       · Phosphorus       · Vitamin A, E, C, K Silky Apricot Butter Recipe                                           INGREDIENTS       ½ cup Sincerely Nuts Dried Turkish Apricots       ½ cup boiled water       ½ cup salted butter       1 tbsp vanilla extract       1 pinch Celtic or Himalayan sea salt       Place apricots in a shallow bowl, pour boiling water over them and let sit for ½ hour       Place apricots and their soaking water in a food processor. Process on high for 1 minute, until apricots are smoothly pureed. Add butter, vanilla and salt and puree another minute, until all ingredients are well blended. Kosher Quality Delivered Fresh                                           Sincerely Nuts brings unparalleled online convenience, high quality and supreme value to all of our delicious dried fruits, nuts,