        (220, 'GERBS Super 5 Dried Fruit Snack Mix 2 LBS. Premium | Top 14 Food Allergy Free | Resealable Bulk Bag | Made in USA | Dried Blueberry Cranberry Cherry Raisin Goji Berries Trail Mix | Gluten Peanut Free', 'GERBS Store', 'From the brand Allergy Friendly Foods Our story How we got our start                             Our parents always encouraged all-natural, made-from-scratch cooking.  In 2003, we made our pumpkin seeds for a Halloween party. They were an instant hit!  As our friends gobbled them down, we realized our passion for sharing healthy snacks with the people we love.  In that moment, Gerbs was born!      What makes our product unique                             Our products are the safest and most nutritious because we manufacture on our 100% dedicated roasting & packaging equipment. Our entire product line is Top 14 food allergy free from the following: gluten, wheat, peanuts, tree nuts, soy, dairy, eggs, fish, shellfish, crustacean, mustard & sesame.      Why we love what we do                             Gerbs makes healthy foods that you will feel good feeding to your family. Our mission is to provide delicious foods that can be eaten safely by those affected by severe food allergies. There is nothing artificial about Gerbs. Our products are non-gmo & free from preservatives, trans-fat, and MSG. Product Description Gerbs Super 5 Dried Fruit Mix - Cranberry, Raisin, Goji Berry, Blueberry and Cherry       A POCKET FULL OF POWER. You can be a superhero 24/7 with this balanced blend of sweet, delicious chewiness and fortifying nutrition. Unsulfured (sulfur dioxide has been identified as a key problematic substance involved with allergic reaction to sulfite in foods) and containing no added preservatives, dried through the nutrient-saving evaporation process.       Super 5 dried fruit mix was sourced by the purchasing team at Gerbs who partner with the world’s top dedicated allergen-free farms that harvest in dedicated facilities, on dedicated equipment, so there is no risk of the top food allergens and/or cross-contamination. Our goal at Gerbs is to give the allergen conscious community peace of mind when choosing products for themselves and their families.       SUPER 5 DRIED FRUIT MIX INGREDIENTS: Cranberries (pure cane sugar, sunflower oil), Raisins (sunflower oil), Goji berries, Blueberries (pure cane sugar, sunflower oil), Cherries (pure cane sugar, sunflower oil). Gerbs Super 5 Dried Fruit Mix - Unsulfured, No preservatives - Free from the Top 14 Common Food Allergies                                                                              How to Properly Store Gerbs Dried Fruit Mixes                                      STORAGE OF GERBS       We strongly recommend storing in an airtight (dark colored/opaque) container in a cool, dark environment like a pantry or kitchen cabinet, away from direct exposure to sunlight or excessive heat like an oven. During high heat & humidity summer months, you may find it best to store in the refrigerator. The amount of times you open the container and let in the harmful effects of oxygen will only increase the likelihood of rancidity; thus we encourage you to not empty more than 1 pound of product at a time. All Gerbs Lines are Free from the Top 14 recognized Food Allergens                                        All of our raw ingredients are processed, packaged, stored, and shipped by our trained staff in our family owned & operated facility in Johnston, Rhode Island on dedicated non-GMO, Vegan, and Kosher Equipment. For anyone with a mild to severe food allergy or a family with one, we wish to assure you that this is why Gerbs handles all aspects of production & operation, and we are among a handful of companies in the world who can state this. Every Gerbs product is free from gluten, wheat, peanuts, tree nuts, legumes, mustard, sesame, eggs, dairy, soy, lupine, fish, crustacean, shellfish and mustard. Gerbs All-Natural Promise - Vegan - Non GMO - Kosher Promise                                        This is what Gerbs means when we say we are 100% All Natural!       There’s nothing artificial about Gerbs. Our food is free from preservatives, chemicals, nitrates/nitrites, trans-fat, and MSG. Gerbs products are also certified kosher, non-GMO and vegan. Our products are the safest and most nutritious because we handle all aspects of operation – purchasing, production, inspection, storage, and distribution on our 100% dedicated packaging equipment. Unlike other brands, Gerbs does not outsource any aspect of production and/or packaging. Our highly trained and caring staff have your families well-being at heart.       -Sennen & Galen Conte, Owners Gerbs Dried Fruits = The Ultimate Source of Natural Energy, Protein, Essential Vitamins & Minerals, Antioxidants & More Nutritional Panel, Information & Ingredients – Gerbs Super 5 Dried Fruit Mix - 2 Pound Serving Size', 19.99, 28.99, 'In Stock', 'Grocery & Gourmet Food › Produce › Dried Fruits & Vegetables › Dried Fruits › Dried Mixed Fruits', null, '2000-01-01', 'GERBS ALLERGY FRIENDLY FOODS', null, 4.40, 1706, 67, 16, 9, 3, 5),
