        (377, 'Premium Coffee Cascara - Dried Coffee Shells Husk Premium- Ecuadorian Geisha Coffee Sun Dried Cascara Fruit Tea (Loose Leaves)', 'Brand: Mont Coffee', 'From the brand Coffee is our passion.                                        From Premium Specialty Gesha to Coffee Cherry Husk, we are all about Coffee and its unparalleled qualities. Ethically sourced. Previous page How did we get our start?                                        In 2020, Felipe Altamirano and Gabriela Toral combined their passion for quality coffee into a venture that connected them closely with small-scale producers. They didnt just source premium beans; they also explored innovative uses for coffee beans and fruit, emphasizing quality and deep connections with the small farms at the core of their business. What makes our products unique?                                        Coffee from Ecuadors distinct regions like the Galapagos Islands and Loja. Quality is ensured by meticulously checking all batches and guaranteeing a premium product. Our products. Specialty Pods now available!                                        Mont Coffee makes sure to keep up with your busy day. Our pods are compatible with all original coffee brewing machines. Next page Product Description Whole Bean and Ground Ecuadorian Specialty Coffee from 5 Top Coffee Producing Regions in Ecuador. From the towering mountains in the middle of the world to the unique Galapagos Islands, each coffee bean from the 5 distinct regions brings the true essence of Ecuador.       MONT COFFEE: A Journey Through Ecuadors Finest Coffee       Embark on a sensory adventure with MONT COFFEE, a brand born out of the passion and dedication of Felipe Altamirano and Gabriela Toral, two Ecuadorian coffee enthusiasts. Their unwavering love for coffee led them on a quest to unveil the captivating stories hidden within each cup of specialty coffee.       ​       At MONT COFFEE, we believe in honoring the unsung heroes of the coffee world—the farmers and their communities, the guardians of the small, picturesque coffee farms nestled amidst Ecuadors breathtaking landscapes. From the towering mountains in the heart of the world to the enchanting Galapagos Islands, the lush coastal regions, and the mystical Amazon rainforest, each sip of our coffee embodies the essence of Ecuador. Mont Coffee Ecuadorian Espresso Coffee Pod Variety Pack, Compatible w/Nesspresso Original Line System Machine and other Brewers Specialty Coffee Pods Experience the rich and diverse flavors of Ecuadorian coffee with Mont Coffee Specialty Coffee Pods.Choose from three distinct varieties and roast levels: Manabí - Dark Roast, Galápagos - Medium Roast, and Amazonian - Light Roast.Compatible with Original Nespresso Machines for convenient and hassle-free brewing.Elevate your coffee experience with each cup, capturing the essence of Ecuadors finest coffee beans. Arabica Ground Coffee infused with Lions Mane Mushroom Introducing Mont Coffee Specialty Ground Arabica, a unique blend combining premium single-origin Arabica beans from Ecuadors Loja region with the enriching essence of Lions Mane Mushroom. Responsibly sourced and expertly crafted, this fusion offers a delicious balance of energy and focus. Savor the smooth richness of Arabica coffee, subtly enhanced by the earthy notes of Lions Mane Mushroom. Elevate your coffee experience with Mont Coffees 12oz pack, perfect for those seeking a flavorful and revitalizing brew. Coffee Cascara - Coffee Husk - Coffee Cherries ready to be infused. Fresh Announcement! Introducing Mont Coffee Ecuador Coffee Cascara! Perfect for infusions, enjoy the unique sweetness of coffee cherry husks sourced from Ecuador. Straight from the heart of Ecuadors coffee farms, experience the essence of Ecuador in every sip. Discover the rich flavors of Mont Coffee Ecuador Coffee Cascara!       Why Cascara?       Coffee cascara is a total game-changer! Think of it as the sweet sidekick to your regular coffee routine. Its made from the dried husks of coffee cherries and brings this amazing combo of coffee richness and fruity vibes, like a party in your cup! Plus, its got a bit of caffeine kick, though significantly less than your usual coffee fix. Best part? Its super versatile, perfect for whipping up all sorts of tasty infusions, whether youre into hot brews or chilled treats.', 16.54, 16.54, 'Only 3 left in stock - order soon.', 'Grocery & Gourmet Food › Beverages › Tea › Fruit & Herbal Tea › Fruit Tea', '5.51 x 1.97 x 7.87 inches; 3.17 ounces', '2000-01-01', 'Mont Coffee', 'Ecuador', 0.00, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
