        (699, 'SDADI Authorized Height Adjustable Giant 4-in-a-Row Connect Game - Jumbo 4-to-Score with Golf Game Set for Kids and Adults, Indoor/Outdoor Family Floor Game with Quick-Release Slider, White and Blue', 'Brand: GUIDTOP', 'The Jumbo 4-To-Score game is the perfect addition to children’s birthday parties, professional or collegiate tailgates, bars, family reunions, and more. This durable, life-sized version of the classic ring-dropping challenge brings excitement to any event as players strive to align four pieces in a row in any direction. Both kids and adults will enjoy this oversized board game, which not only provides endless fun but also enhances strategic thinking and critical skills. ​​Game play Guide (1)Two players (or teams) drop rings in from the top of the board alternating turns trying to get 4 in a row. To win you or your team must be the first to connect your 4 color rings in a row either horizontally, vertically, or diagonally! (2)Simply slide out the bottom bar when finished to release the rings. Store the rings on the ring holder when finished playing. (3)This upgraded version height adjustable jumbo yard game suitable for both children and adults. It measures from 36 to 49 inches tall. (4)The upgraded version of large Four Connect Game features a sturdy base, reducing the risk of shaking or tipping over for enhanced safety. The base includes golf holes, allowing you to experience another enjoyment with the complimentary set of golf club and golf ball we provide. ​​WARNING (1)Always setup on a flat, even surface. Do not allow children to hang or climb on the game. Doing so may cause the game to tip over causing bodily harm. (2)Recommended for ages 3+. Adult supervision required. (3)If you need to move the assembled game, the game must be lifted by the legs by 2 people (one on each side).', 59.99, 0.00, 'In Stock', 'Toys & Games › Games & Accessories › Floor Games', null, '2000-01-01', 'GUIDTOP', 'China', 3.50, 9, 41, 17, 12, 15, 16),
        (700, 'Hasbro Gaming Guess Who? People & Pets Board Game Edition | The Original Guessing Game for Girls & Boys | Ages 6+ (Amazon Exclusive)', 'Hasbro Gaming Store', 'Bring back childhood memories and introduce the iconic guessing game to your kids and grandkids with the Guess Who? board game. This edition is double the fun because it includes people as well as pets character cards. Each player chooses a mystery character card and then using "yes "or "no" questions, tries to figure out the other players mystery person or pet, depending on which set of cards they use. Players can ask questions about a persons appearance such as "Do they wear glasses?" or whether a pet wears a collar, or purrs. Challenge other players to a series of games and see who can be the first to win 5 games. The Guess Who? game is for 2 players, and makes a great indoor activity for kids ages 6 and up.Hasbro Gaming and all related trademarks and logos are trademarks of Hasbro, Inc.', 16.99, 19.00, 'In Stock', 'Toys & Games › Games & Accessories › Board Games', '1.61 x 10.51 x 10.51 inches', '2000-01-01', 'Hasbro', 'USA', 4.60, 5441, 79, 11, 5, 2, 3),
