        (763, 'Harmony House Backpacking Soup and Chili Kit (Unseasoned) – 18 Count Variety Pack, Resealable Zip Pouches, For Cooking, Camping, Emergency Supply and More', 'Harmony House Store', 'Product Description Conquer the great outdoors on a full belly with our travel-friendly pack of instant mixes                                      At Harmony House Foods we know that whether you’re preparing our dehydrated soups while backpacking, hiking or camping outdoors, or whether you’re serving them from your table at home, quality matters. That’s why you won’t find any of our instant mixes hiding behind flashy labels, colored bags or inside cans. We package all of our soup and chili mixes in clear packaging so you can see the quality for yourself. The vibrant colors mean all of our vegetables are dried at the peak of their freshness and flavor.       Not only will you love the rich, flavorful taste of our Harmony House soup and chili mixes, you’ll love the convenience too! Each pack contains a great time-saving recipe for your kitchen that you’ll be proud to serve to your family for dinner or as a quick-and-easy, wholesome meal for your kids. There’s no need to chop the onions, dice the carrots, or cut the tomatoes. The work has already been done for you! Packed in a lightweight, resealable bags, it’s super convenient for backpacking, hiking and camping. And because it’s dehydrated, it’s a must-have on your emergency-preparedness supply shelf. Packed at the peak of freshness                                  We use a special air-drying process to preserve the nutritional content of our non-GMO ingredients. Our food is free from pesticides, chemicals, and heavy metals.                                        100% Natural        Vegetarian       Gluten-free       No artificial flavorings       Non-GMO       No preservatives       Sourced from local farms A mouthwatering mix of soups and chilis ready for your next adventure                                           Eating